tity other than via explicit, legal means"], n4sch__name:"DeFactoControllingInterestParty"}}, {uri:"https://spec.edmcouncil.org/fibo/ontology/BE/OwnershipAndControl/ControlParties/JointControllingParty", properties:{n4sch__label:["joint controlling party"], n4sch__definition:["party that collectively has the authority to control the affairs of some business organization"], n4sch__name:"JointControllingParty"}}, {uri:"https://spec.edmcouncil.org/fibo/ontology/BE/OwnershipAndControl/ControlParties/InvestmentBasedDeFactoControl", properties:{n4sch__label:["investment-based de facto control"], n4sch__definition:["control that arises through some investment in some entity, other than via the holding of constitutional equity (shares etc.) in that entity"], n4sch__name:"InvestmentBasedDeFactoControl"}}, {uri:"https://spec.edmcouncil.org/fibo/ontology/BE/OwnershipAndControl/ControlParties/Receiver", properties:{n4sch__label:["receiver"], n4sch__definition:["party appointed by some court for the purposes of winding up the affairs of some entity which is no longer solvent"], n4sch__name:"Receiver"}}, {uri:"https://spec.edmcouncil.org/fibo/ontology/BE/OwnershipAndControl/ControlParties/SoleControllingParty", properties:{n4sch__label:["sole controlling party"], n4sch__definition:["party that has sole control over and directs the affairs of some legal entity"], n4sch__name:"SoleControllingParty"}}] AS row
